print("Welcome to the tip calculator!")
Totalbill = float(input("What was the total bill?\n$"))
tip = int(input("How much tip would you like to give?10,12,15?\n"))
num_people = int(input("How many to split the bill?\n"))
Bill_perperson = (((Totalbill*(tip*0.01)+Totalbill)/num_people))
print(f"Each person should pay: $ {round(Bill_perperson,3)}")            # {round(Bill_perperson, 3)} gives round figure of the bill per person with rounding done upto 3 digits

OUTPUT 
Welcome to the tip calculator!
What was the total bill?
$269.97
How much tip would you like to give?10,12,15?
12
How many to split the bill?
3
Each person should pay: $ 100.789 
